  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Rinse lentils, soak 30 minutes, then drain.",
    "In a bowl, mix lentils, olive oil, and brine, seasoning with pepper.",
    "Spread the mixture onto a parchment-lined baking sheet.",
    "Roast for 25 minutes, stirring halfway through.",
    "While roasting, combine wine, onion, garlic, tomatoes, lemon zest, juice, and oregano in a small saucepan; simmer for 5 minutes until aromatic.",
    "Remove lentils from oven and pour sauce over them; stir to coat.",
    "Return to oven for 5 more minutes until sauce thickens slightly.",
    "Let the dish rest 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Garnish with extra oregano if desired."
  ],
